n8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010045, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my God, in the name of all those who have besought you and in the name of all those who have prayed to you in lands and seas (please do) bless Muhammad and his Household, bestow upon the poor among the believing men and women with wealth and fortune, upon the ailed believing men and women with healing and health, upon the living believing men and women with kindness and generosity, upon the dead believing men and women with forgiveness and mercy, and upon the emigrant believing men and women with returning them home peacefully and successfully, in the name of Muhammad and the members of his Household.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mere Ma’bood! Uska waasta jo Tujh se raaz kehta hai aur uska waasta jo Tujhe sehra o dariya mein pukaarta hai. Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki Aal (a.s) par durood bhej keh muflis momeneen o momenaat ko maal o sarwat ataa kar, bimaar momin mardo’n aur momin aurto’n ko sahet o tandurasti ataa farma, zindah momin mardo’n aur momin aurto’n par apna lutf o karam aur farwaani farma aur marhoom momin mardo’n aur momin aurto’n par bakhshish aur maher-baani ataa farma aur musaafir momin mardo’n aur momin aurto’n ko sahet o salaamati aur maal ke saath apne gharo’n mein pohoncha de. Tujhe waasta hai Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki tamaam Aale paak (a.s) ka.", "Urdu": "میرے معبود! اس کا واسطہ جو تجھ سے راز کہتا ہے اور اس کاواسطہ جو تجھے صحرا ور دریا میں پکارتا ہے محمد ؐ اور ان کی آل پر درود بھیج کہ مفلس مومنین ومومنات کو مال و ثروت عطا کر،بیمار مومن مردوں اور مومن عورتوں کو صحت و تندرستی عطا فرما، زندہ مومنین اور مومنات پر اپنا لطف و کرم اور فراوانی فرما اور مرحوم مومنین اور مومنات پر بخشش اور مہربانی عطا فرما اور مسافر مومنین اور مومنات کو صحت و سلامتی اور مال کے ساتھ اپنے گھروں میں پہنچا دے تجھے واسطہ ہے محمد ؐاوران کی تمام آلؑ پاک کا۔", "RArabic": "ELAAHI BEHAQQE MAN NAAJAAK. WA BEHAQQE MAN DA-A’AKA FIL BARRE WAL BAHR. SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALEH. WA TAFAZZAL A’LAA FOQARAA-IL MOAMENEENA WAL MOA-MENAATE BIL GHENAA WAS SEA’H. WA A’LAA MARZAL MOAMENEENA WAL MOA-MENAATE BISH SHEFAA-E WAS SHE-HATE WAR RAAHAH. WA A’LAA AHYAA-IL MOA-MENEENA WAL MOA-MENAATE BIL LUTFE WAL KARAAMAH. WA A’LAA AMWAATIL MOA-MENEENA WAL MOA-MENAATE BIL MAGHFERATE WAR RAHMAH. WA A’LAA GHORABAA-IL MOA-MENEENA WAL MOA-MENAATE BIR RADDI ELAA AWTAANEHIM SAALEMEENA GHAANEMEENA BEHAQQE MOHAMMADIN WA AALEHI AJMAE’EN.", "ArabicText1": "اِلٰهِيْ بِحَقِّ مَنْ نَاجَاكَ وَبِحَقِّ مَنْ دَعَاكَ فِي الْبَرِّ وَالْبَحْرِ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَتَفَضَّلْ عَلٰى فُقَرَاءِ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ بِالْغَنَاءِ وَالثَّرْوَةِ وَعَلٰى مَرْضَى الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ بِالشِّفَاءِ وَالصِّحَّةِ وَعَلٰى اَحْيَاءِ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ بِاللُّطْفِ وَالْكَرَمِ وَعَلٰى اَمْوَاتِ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ بِالْمَغْفِرَةِ وَالرَّحْمَةِ وَعَلٰى غُرَبَاءِ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ بِالرَّدِّ اِلٰى اَوْطَانِهِمْ سَالِمِيْنَ غَانِمِيْنَ بِمُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِهٖ اَجْمَعِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign1